<br>
As a gag, I run behind the mage's epic pet.<br>
<br>
The mob, instead of nuking me, charges.<br>
<br>
I do this about 10 times and in every case, the mob charges as though it can't see me.<br>
<br>
Maybe the mobs were out of mana, maybe not.<br>
<br>
Opinions?<br>
